{"tid":2441170,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【緬甸政變】軍警四出拘捕罷工參與者 變節警指上級下令「射死抗爭者」","createTime":"2021-03-10T13:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T17:58:53.000Z","uid":48083,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9b67001af6aabda5e565c24484b3f15b7aced68c","tid":2441170,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T13:03:18.000Z","msg":"..此外，有變節到印度的緬甸前警察向路透社透露，他上月底在西部城鎮坎巴（Khampat）執勤，被上級要求以半自動步槍鎮壓抗爭者，「直至射到他們死為止」，但27歲的塔彭（Tha Peng）決定拒絕執行命令。上級翌日再問他會否開槍，他再次拒絕並決定辭職。<br />\n<br />\n塔彭加入緬甸警隊已有9年。塔彭表示，他辭職後回家，但因為擔心自己會被拘捕，於是漏夜離開家鄉，逃亡至印度。他指出，根據緬甸警例，警察只可以使用橡膠子彈對待示威者，而且對膝頭以下的位置開槍，但上級當日的指令顯然不符警例。<br />\n<br />\n路透社指出，塔彭是首批辭職及逃亡前往印度的警察，而塔彭披露當日還有6名同袍一起拒絕執行上級的開槍命令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/mr-rail-03102021064050.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fmr-rail-03102021064050.html&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPsg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=545d4c77\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/mr-rail-03102021064050.html</a>"},{"pid":"cea568bde8cd9a8dcee32e1d4b602a16ba20397e","tid":2441170,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T13:15:52.000Z","msg":"誠懇呼籲唔好再舉美國旗，你唔係美國人又搞佢哋支旗，美國人會好反感<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319023\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319023</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fb4a909c35975c60415e66be927486790d9911e7","tid":2441170,"uid":393145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T13:21:02.000Z","msg":"香港犬開槍：洗唔洗whatsapp通知你呀？"},{"pid":"2ca048024cbecf6b70893a541e0bb949b7e7d7e8","tid":2441170,"uid":108606,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T13:21:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/popo-02_Tb2Oa_600x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fpopo-02_Tb2Oa_600x0.png&h=abde282e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<